Name: Anime Manga Style Girl - Color By Number Pixel Art Coloring
About the game: This is a coloring game with 54 different anime-style illustrations. - How to Play - 1. Select a picture. 2. Zoom the image with the mouse wheel until you can see the numbers in the box. 3. Left-click to select a color and paint the same number as the number. (Hold down the left mouse button to paint in a continuous sequence.)
